targets.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(sum("rx_bytes"), 1s) AS "Rx", non_negative_derivative(sum("tx_bytes"), 1s) AS "Tx" FROM "usg_wan_ports" WHERE ("device_name" =~ /^UDM-Pro$/ AND "site_name" =~ /^(Default \(default\)|Maison \(default\))$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "purpose"
